_json.gridTitle: Build an All Season Outdoor Cat Habitat
_json.description: [Early November 2012 - Mr. Max peeks into the house from the habitat] It was in the spring of 2007 when our beloved Mr. Spanky (A.K.A. Houdini) escaped once again; this time by jumping from an open upstairs window. Fortunately a week later a kind neighbor responded to our flyer and we were reunited. Because he is an indoor cat, we worried about his safety since we live in an area that has many predators and occasional traffic that keep the neighborhood pretty clear of stray cats.
